{
  "stem": "9701.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was born on August 15, 1924, in Freiburg, which is in southwest Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "F-R-E-I-B-- as in boy-- U-R-G.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I lived in a village named Kippenheim, K-I-P-P-E-N-H-E-I-M, which is about 40 kilometers north of Freiburg.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my family on my father's side of the family had lived in Kippenheim for many, many generations.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother, or my mother's family, also had lived in Germany for many generations, but in another part of Germany.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother came from Hanau, H-A-N-A-U, which is near Frankfurt, F-R-A-N-K-F-U-R-T.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was an only child.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My father was-- had a business, which he operated together with his younger brother, Oskar, O-S-K-A-R.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a business that my great-grandfather started in 1857.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was a dry good business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Over the years, the focus of the business changed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Initially, it was a store.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But later on, I-- we also dealt with customers that were-- lived in other parts of Germany.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in fact, I know my father, once a year, made a business trip to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So there must have been some businesses assoc-- association there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I did not know until I was six years old that I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My family was a non-practicing family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We went to synagogue on the high holy days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I had also been to church with our housekeeper.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I didn't really know the difference.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was just another place to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her name was Paula, P-A-U-L-A.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I entered first grade, at that time in Germany, religion was taught as part of the regular curriculum.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was probably during the first week in school that the teacher said, the next hour is going to be religious instructions.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
